@startuml AITTA Architecture
skinparam backgroundColor #FEFEFE
skinparam package {
  BackgroundColor #E1F5FE
  BorderColor #01579B
  BorderThickness 2
}
skinparam note {
  BackgroundColor #FFF3E0
  BorderColor #E65100
}

title AITTA Architecture Diagram

package "Enterprise IT Environment" as ENT #E1F5FE {
  [Splunk]
  [ServiceNow]
  [Jira]
  [CMDB]
  [Monitoring Tools]
}

package "MCP Layer" as MCP #F3E5F5 {
  [Model Context Protocol]
  note right : • Standardized Integration\n• Tool Discovery\n• Secure Communication
}

package "AITTA Agent Core" as CORE #E8F5E8 {
  package "AI Planning Engine" as AI {
    [LLM Analysis]
    [Priority Logic]
    [Decision Making]
  }
  package "Orchestration Layer" as ORCH {
    [State Management]
    [Error Recovery]
    [Audit Logging]
  }
}

package "Data Persistence" as DB #FFF3E0 {
  [SQLAlchemy ORM]
  [SQLite/PostgreSQL]
  [Migration Scripts]
  [Audit Trail Storage]
}

ENT --> MCP : integrates via
MCP --> AI : provides data to
MCP --> ORCH : orchestrates with
AI --> DB : stores analysis
ORCH --> DB : persists state

note as WORKFLOW #FCE4EC
  **Workflow Process:**
  Monitor → Analyze → Enrich → Decide → Act → Audit
end note

WORKFLOW .. DB : results stored

@enduml
